Module fitnessclubgui.fitnessclub
Package fitnessclubgui.fitnessclub

Class FitnessClass

java.lang.Object
fitnessclubgui.fitnessclub.FitnessClass
public class FitnessClass extends Object
This class contains information of a fitness class A fitness class contains the type of class, the instructor, the location, the time, and the attending members and guests
Author:
Francisco Marquez

    • FitnessClass

      public FitnessClass(Offer classInfo, Instructor instructor, Location studio, Time time)
      Initalizes a Fitness Class object
      Parameters:
      classInfo - The type of class being offered, can be Pilates, Spinning, or Cardio
      instructor - The name of the instructor, can be Jennifer, Kim, Denise, Davis, or Emma
      studio - The location of the fitness class
      time - The time of the fitness class, can be morning, afternoon, or night
